creator: Wintrust Community Banks
descriptionHtml:
.COMmunity Mobile is a mobile banking service for Lake Forest Bank & Trust and its other community bank locations: Highland Park Bank & Trust, Bank of Highwood Ft. Sheridan and North Chicago Community Bank.

.COMmunity Mobile app helps you manage your money quickly and easily — anytime, anywhere. Whether checking your balance, depositing a check, paying a bill or transferring funds, it delivers a new level of speed and convenience.

Feature List:
Accounts
Transfers
Bill Pay
Zelle®
Mobile Check Deposit
Cardless Cash
Card Controls
Personal Finance
descriptionShort: Lake Forest Bank and Trust .COMmunity MOBILE
